'\"macro stdmacro
.TH SAVEDESKTOP 1W
.SH NAME
savedesktop \- saves colors in \f2~/.desktop\fP
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B savedesktop
.SH DESCRIPTION
\f2savedesktop\f1 saves colors in indexes 0 and 7-15 for use as text, 
border, and background colors.
.I makemap
uses these color assignments.
.SH SEE ALSO
showmap(1W),
makemap(1W)
.SH FILES
~/.desktop
